        Create a JSON Reimbursement by specifying the primary key (receivable and reimbursing item keys) and the two amounts. Status defaults to EXISTING.
        Parameters:
        receivableItemKey - the key for the receivable item (part of primary key)
        reimbursingItemKey - the key for the reimbursing item (part of primary key)
        reimbursedAmount - the amount of the receivable reimbursed by the reimbursing item
        allocatedAmount - the amount of the receivable allocated by the reimbursing item transaction
